{"tid":951028,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國駐香港總領事館領事部，近日探訪了於泰國、印尼、菲律賓及台灣的BN(O)在囚人士。","createTime":"2018-12-22T04:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T11:33:51.000Z","uid":6435,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d4be38ffb00d6b3a1d0c5c3074d4ddd8a7fc3bf4","tid":951028,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T04:06:46.000Z","msg":"Consular staff from the British Consulate-General in Hong Kong had recently visited British National (Overseas) prisoners in Thailand, Indonesia, the Philippines and Taiwan.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">These joint visits have allowed 40 BN(O) prisoners to meet Cantonese-speaking British consular officers and discuss any matters of concern. </span>Staff from the British Consulate-General are also able to relay messages from family members in Hong Kong and distribute local Chinese magazines. <span style=\"color: red;\">Consular staff can also use their visits to check on prisoners&rsquo; health and welfare - particularly in detention facilities where standards are lower than in the UK or Hong Kong.</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/hong-kong-consular-staff-reach-out-to-british-national-overseas-prisoners-in-the-region\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong-consular-staff-reach-out-to-british-national-overseas-prisoners-in-the-region&d=pK2oF7PWZi%2FXTPe7b0RN5gEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=bdc563ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/news/hong-kong-consular-staff-reach-out-to-british-national-overseas-prisoners-in-the-region</a>"},{"pid":"e13f7c2a2f4f356da56f17435d251581a9f9b60d","tid":951028,"uid":6435,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T04:20:13.000Z","msg":"CHILD登連咁簡單既英文都無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d5d5f118844e07d9af2c2fb78b84f